	Rule: Download
	------
	Otavio R. Piske
	------
	Jan, 2013

Description

	Downloads a file

Element 

	Name: download

Attributes

	url: the URL to file to download
	overwrite: whether to overwrite a previously downloaded file of the same name
	
Example

----------------------------------------
<download url="http://orpiske.net/ssps/files/0.1.x/${name}-${version}-bin.tar.bz2"
  			overwrite="false" />
----------------------------------------